title: Who serves the best apple cider doughnuts in New Hampshire?
text:
Who serves the best apple cider doughnuts in New Hampshire? Published 5:00 AM EDT Oct 09, 2015 A Large Text Photos 
WMUR.com wants to know the very best things in New Hampshire in our weekly segment called WMUR Viewers' Choice. 
This week, we want to know where to find the best apple cider doughnuts in New Hampshire! Please, do not nominate national chains. 
Leave a comment below with your nomination or cast your vote on our Facebook page . 
Voting ends each Thursday at 9 a.m.! 
Businesses, consider sharing the following graphics on Facebook ( download a .jpg ) and Twitter ( download a .jpg ) to encourage your customers to vote!
